{"tid":876290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛新覺羅後裔在日本成為眼科專科醫師","createTime":"2018-10-25T13:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T23:32:32.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4fa71cfcf61bc8a42c00bb2323f6fd5622d0e5","tid":876290,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"有日本網媒在大井町駅，見到呢個看似普通的廣告牌。卻被院長醫生的名字吸引-愛新覺羅&middot;維。番查之下，証實確是清末王朝的後裔，在Facebook名字亦用漢語拼音wei.aixinjueluo。網媒又找來溥儀的皇后婉容的相片對照，說有幾分神似。<br />\n<br />\n據診所的資料顯示，愛新覺羅&middot;維畢業於名古屋大學醫科，之後取得東京大學大學院博士學位,在醫院工作一段時間後開設自己的眼科診所。<br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得佢可能係溥傑和日本人妻子嵯峨浩的後裔，十幾年前常盤貴子演出劇集「流転の王妃」時，說過她的同班同學就是溥傑的孫女。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/41/84/qJeVnaCZmKScraU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F41%2F84%2FqJeVnaCZmKScraU.jpg&h=cd331117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://netgeek.biz/archives/129789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnetgeek.biz%2Farchives%2F129789&d=M2bG9fiv1H7O7mhUogrt4S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5e765d9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://netgeek.biz/archives/129789</a>"},{"pid":"8881f97dc4df1b84fbc4b3bd4fef2b1e1adfa6fe","tid":876290,"uid":21545,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"中國皇帝後人係日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b419b3a494220f37d18aa7f2ee3da82356489c9f","tid":876290,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"嫮生與福永健治結婚，婚後更名為「福永嫮生」。福永家和嵯峨家有深交，健治是嫮生姨丈的侄兒，同時其父系祖先可遠溯至宇多天皇。兩人育有五名子女：長女雅子，就職於東京的三井不動產；長男福永恆明，在豐田自動車就職；次子福永行良曾於北海道的福祉學校學習；三子福永浩伸，在父親的老人公寓幫忙；次女典子曾於武庫川女子大學藥學部就讀。其中行良曾在北京第二外國語學院留學兩年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bde9e204843412ea07e7ddd94fcba40b38ac85e","tid":876290,"uid":35014,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afa7a365accdbf334ca5752164284a413254e91d","tid":876290,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"做日本人好過做支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3a2fe19830c4106a4772cb3f7c45e835844b24","tid":876290,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"滿州國？"},{"pid":"47f362d70db8074db581323e2eb0cc56ab4a1ad3","tid":876290,"uid":37389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"溥儀眼鏡仲唔重金請佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21dfcc1eeddf80f53f98d073e4e0f253a04e3a1","tid":876290,"uid":49197,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.puyi.com/api/image_resize/locator_resize.php?s=/uploads/images/puyi_tst%20centre_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.puyi.com%2Fapi%2Fimage_resize%2Flocator_resize.php%3Fs%3D%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2Fpuyi_tst%2520centre_1.jpg&h=e2a165d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e1c54e395b6cad0a7ef2b7d460229c23700365","tid":876290,"uid":127988,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"afa7a365accdbf334ca5752164284a413254e91d","tid":876290,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"做日本人好過做支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"愛新覺羅唔係改晒姓金咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清亡以後族人為防止身份遭到危險大多改姓，現今發展大致分為以下情況：<br />\n<br />\n取漢姓：按照清帝退位時的規定條款（《清室優待條件》），嫡系後裔主要都採用其滿語中的「黃金」之意改姓「金」，如現任家族首領金毓嶂及父親金友之。<br />\n也有其他選擇艾、羅、肇、趙等。<br />\n直接棄用：表示對皇族後裔身份避而不談，如大書法家啟功，直接以名字中的「啟」為姓。<br />\n保留或恢復原姓者：表示對皇族後裔的身份為榮：如愛新覺羅&middot;毓嶦、愛新覺羅&middot;啟驤、演員愛新覺羅&middot;啟星、女畫家愛新覺羅&middot;毓崌等。<br />\n不過也由於無法確認血脈真偽，因此出現了許多藉機攀附的「冒姓者」。<br />\n家族世系譜"},{"pid":"c7201a22f20700df938e68201f4ae4b46e50f9c0","tid":876290,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"九龍城果頭果個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d7341ea4c630a34d28ff10dfabc9a04199f692","tid":876290,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/006mhoeVgy70iiMd006de\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs15.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F006mhoeVgy70iiMd006de&h=b5908756&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dce5ea1580fbdd537a59fc414c8e2edf9e0994bb","tid":876290,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"滿日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b44830debeea32bb2c8c943254d3b5f2437eb","tid":876290,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"偽滿州國"},{"pid":"03c6f6b4a8e9ffa9358b3681c20406dfb477da6a","tid":876290,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8881f97dc4df1b84fbc4b3bd4fef2b1e1adfa6fe","tid":876290,"uid":21545,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"中國皇帝後人係日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"好似唔少皇朝後人都去左日本，例如劉邦後人。"},{"pid":"a29076f383393705a08cffc6f9d1b8a8bd0afd92","tid":876290,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31f4ecc10e91f5a53e3f3a06677aef9f50d80295","tid":876290,"uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8881f97dc4df